  <summary>2/26/1987--Introduced.
Prohibits the contracting out for performance by private contractor personnel of any function at an arsenal or weapons manufacturing facility under the jurisdiction of the Department of Defense. Provides an exception to such prohibition for functions currently under contract.</summary>
